The battle is over. Tyrael looks around. His ship is gone, but backup 
is here. he also has some great data with him. He turns to Rodimus and 
Magnus.

Tyrael: Rodimus, I must leave. You were a worthy ally, but I fear the 
next time we meet we shall be enemies.

He offered his hand.
